                <h1>Who Is the Main Character in "The Yellow Wallpaper"?</h1>
                <p>The main character of "The Yellow Wallpaper" is a woman who remains unnamed throughout the story. Often referred to simply as the narrator, she is a new mother suffering from postpartum depression. Her descent into mental illness is depicted through her obsession with the wallpaper in her confinement room, reflecting her struggles with autonomy and identity.</p>
